	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_ECONOMIC_UNION_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Ever Closer Union</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_ECONOMIC_UNION_HELP">
			<Text>As we have made it our goal to unite the forces of Freedom, it is essential that we seek to share our resources and bind ourselves closer together.[NEWLINE]Which approach is most pressing?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_ECONOMIC_UNION_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Accept the loss of {1_YieldCost} in order to generate +1 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism from Customs Houses, Harbors, and Airports.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_ECONOMIC_UNION_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>All [ICON_GREAT_MERCHANT] Merchants generate -2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold, but all Farms and Plantations generate +1 [ICON_GOLD].</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_ECONOMIC_UNION_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Trade away 4 [ICON_RES_OIL] to receive a Guided Missile in every City.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_ECONOMIC_UNION_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Free movement of peoples will globalise our world and bring about a lasting peace. We have more in common than that which divides us.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_ECONOMIC_UNION_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>By banding together into one block, our trading power will see to it that only those aligned with our interests may profit. With control like that, peace will surely follow.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_ECONOMIC_UNION_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>The only way to ensure peace is to make the prospect of war so ugly that no one would dare begin one.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
